- cs.PF (Performance) is relevant as the paper analyzes the miss ratio of data item requests. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is possible as caching systems are often used in networking applications. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also possible as the paper deals with a distributed hash table.
